page.title: 09MY VALLAGE
page.content: My real name is Katherine. I live at 7 Windmill Cottages with my Mum, Dad and two sisters. My dad has just got a job in Strood, working for Tesco's Supermarket and gets up at 5 am. I get up at 7.45 am. For breakfast I have cereals with tea or milk to drink. Sometimes I have toast with marmite. I leave for Stoke School at 8.50 am. and my sister Joanne catches a bus to Allhallows at 9.05 am. I bring a packed lunch to school. Most people have school dinners. At school I do English and Mathematics and Art & Craft with games and TV programmes. We also sing and do other things. I like working Fletcher Maths best of all. We have lunch from 12 o'clock until 1.10 pm.
